{"tid":457962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟佢有冇friendzone我","createTime":"2017-11-04T11:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T15:57:43.000Z","uid":40286,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9edeef65a5d83faf7cf87a3cb020dbe88bbad7","tid":457962,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"我冇表示過任何野<br />\n身邊人傳左我同佢有野一段時間了<br />\n<br />\n未試過單獨出街<br />\n但經常有個4人組合 2男2女咁周圍去玩<br />\n<br />\n不時有whatsapp <br />\n一方面會好強調佢已經當左我係姊妹<br />\n但另一方面又同人講如果同我單獨出街嘅話會好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n如果佢friendzone左我 咁又點會尷尬<br />\n咁多位巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問絲打 樣子真係咁重要？<br />\n我自問唔靚仔 算係中下樣 <br />\n但勝在健談 成日講野氹到身邊人笑<br />\n<br />\n利申A2"},{"pid":"0d754cc9c706b9f3be3233407761e26fce424ede","tid":457962,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"兵"},{"pid":"6d01a3bbb9d8c5b80bbbd3753a64a886aa8f3c11","tid":457962,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7bcddaa11151b13cc6c55ddaa99b334c9cd701","tid":457962,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"一開始無feel 就係無feel"},{"pid":"33a8580370010300ce48003a89dbe7035644d671","tid":457962,"uid":70028,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"你個樣令佢尷尬"},{"pid":"f2ae459691bdb27f5b56cb6db694e2b38258ccad","tid":457962,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"同我有d似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a706a375b67e321bbc791f1aa35b9873ed15dd","tid":457962,"uid":129086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"Friendzone左啦 當你